---
// Hero Section with American Flag background
---

<section class="hero-section relative bg-navy text-white py-16 md:py-28 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Flag background with hard light filter -->
  <div class="flag-bg"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="mb-6 animate-fadeUp">
      <span class="tag tag-dark">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></span>
        For Small & Medium Business Owners
      </span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl leading-tight tracking-tight mb-6 animate-fadeUp delay-1">
      You Follow the Rules.<br />
      <span class="text-red-500">They Write Them.</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="font-body text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mb-10 leading-relaxed animate-fadeUp delay-2">
      You pay your taxes. You follow every regulation. You provide for your employees the best you can. Meanwhile, billionaires and mega-corporations play by a completely different set of rules â€” rules they paid to create. <strong class="text-white">Here's what that's actually costing you.</strong>
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 animate-fadeUp delay-3">
      <a href="#daily-squeeze" class="btn-primary px-6 py-3 text-base inline-block">
        See the Numbers
      </a>
      <a href="#sources" class="bg-white/10 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/20 transition text-base inline-block">
        View All Sources
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
  }

  .flag-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url('/flag.svg');
    background-size: 300% auto;
    background-position: 0% 0%;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    mix-blend-mode: hard-light;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: rotate(180deg);
    transform-origin: center center;
    animation: fadeInFlag 1.5s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.5s;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInFlag {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: rotate(180deg) scale(1.05);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 0.25;
      transform: rotate(180deg) scale(1);
    }
  }
</style>
